Following von Korff et al. (2005), a marker analysis was executed in the general linear model (GLM) procedure of SAS version 9.1 (SAS Institute 2004) by using a 3-factorial analysis of variance (ANOVA) with a mixed hierarchical model in order to detect QTLs associated with seedling and field resistance. The two models applied are: 1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}\usepackage{amsmath}
